{
  "design_notes": "The chart is structured around the 88 BPM synthwave groove. Early bars establish a smooth flowing pattern using alternating left, center, and right lanes (GAP, BAR, NOTE) reflecting the melodic synthesizer contour. We transition into hold notes precisely mapped to major melodic swells at bars 2, 4, 6, 8, and 10. Density carefully tracks the energy curve, ramping up during peak bars and leaving rhythmic breathing room by omitting weaker 16th-note subdivisions to maintain a rewarding casual flow.",
  "sections": [
    {
      "name": "Main Wave",
      "start_bar": 0,
      "intent": "Introduce the player to the clean synthwave flow with gentle 8th-note sweeps, escalating slightly into comfortable hold releases that ground the underlying rhythmic pulses."
    }
